                          PORTAGEshared test-suite

Contents of this directory:

 - unit-testing/        unit test suites that are too slow or too complex to
                        routinely run as part of compilation

 - regress-small-voc/   regression test suite on a small corpus

 - rescoring-example/   example prepared for a previous release of the
                        rescoring code only



